## Open CFPs

<%- @cfps.each do |cfp| -%>
- [<%= cfp.event.name %>](<%= Router.event_cfp_index_path(cfp.event) %>) will be in <%= cfp.event.location %> <%= event_dates_in_sentence(cfp.event) %>. The [CFP](<%= cfp.link %>) closes <%= cfp.formatted_close_date.gsub(/, #{@year}/, "") %>.
<%- end -%>

> None of these feel quite right? Check out our list of [meetup cfps](https://www.rubyevents.org/cfp?kind=meetup)! Many are open year round and always looking for new talks.

## <%= @month %>'s events

<%- @this_month_events.each do |event| -%>
<%- next if event.static_metadata.cancelled? -%>
- [<%= event.name.gsub(/ #{@year}/, "") %>](<%= Router.event_path(event) %>) was in <%= event.location %> <%= event_dates_in_sentence(event) %>. <% if event.talks.watchable.any? %>[Videos are available!](<%= Router.event_videos_path(event) %>)<% end %>
<%- end -%>

> Did you attend a Ruby event this month that isn't on the list? Let us know with an [issue](https://github.com/rubyevents/rubyevents/issues/new) or [PR](https://github.com/rubyevents/rubyevents/blob/main/CONTRIBUTING.md)!

## <%= @next_month %>'s events

<%- @next_month_events.each do |event| -%>
- [<%= event.name %>](<%= Router.event_path(event) %>) will be in <%= event.location %> <%= event_dates_in_sentence(event) %>.<% if event.tickets.url %> [Tickets](<%= event.tickets.url %>) are available for $TICKET_PRICE.<% end %>
<%- end -%>

> Prepare more than a few months ahead by checking out our [calendar](https://www.rubyevents.org/events/<%= @year %>) or the full [list of events](https://www.rubyevents.org/events).

