## Contributions

This month, we merged [XX PRs from XX contributors!](https://github.com/rubyevents/rubyevents/pulls?q=is%3Apr+is%3Amerged+merged%3A<%= @github_date_range %>) XX PRs were [new event data and videos](https://github.com/rubyevents/rubyevents/pulls?q=is%3Apr+is%3Amerged+merged%3A<%= @github_date_range %>+label%3Acontent).

### Big Updates


### Welcome, First-Time Contributors!

A warm welcome to XX developers making their first contribution to RubyEvents!

```bash
comm -13 \
   <(gh pr list --repo RubyEvents/RubyEvents --limit 1000 --state merged \
       --search "merged:<%= @first_day_of_month.iso8601 %>" \
       --json author --jq '[.[].author.login] | unique | sort | .[]') \
   <(gh pr list --repo RubyEvents/RubyEvents --limit 100 --state merged \
       --search "merged:>=<%= @first_day_of_month.iso8601 %>" \
       --json author --jq '[.[].author.login] | unique | sort | .[]') | \
 while read login; do
   gh pr list --repo RubyEvents/RubyEvents --state merged \
     --search "merged:>=<%= @first_day_of_month.iso8601 %> author:$login" \
     --limit 100 --json author,number,createdAt \
     --jq 'sort_by(.createdAt) | .[0] | "[\(.author.name)](https://github.com/RubyEvents/RubyEvents/pull/\(.number))"'
 done
```

### Thank You to All XX Contributors ❤️

```bash
gh pr list --repo RubyEvents/RubyEvents   --limit 100   --state merged   --json author   --search "merged:>=<%= @first_day_of_month.iso8601 %> merged:<=<%= @last_day_of_month.iso8601 %>"   --jq '[group_by(.author.login)[] | {name: .[0].author.name, login: .[0].author.login, count: length}] | sort_by(.count) | reverse[] | "- \(.name) [(@\(.
login))](https://github.com/\(.login)) \(.count) PRs"'
```

> Looking to join this list in July? Check out our [contributions page](https://www.rubyevents.org/contributions) or the [CONTRIBUTING.md](https://github.com/rubyevents/rubyevents/blob/main/CONTRIBUTING.md) in GitHub.
